          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Displays a more natural display of some values, such as zero, where it may be displayed as "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "Zero KB"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", ignoring all other flags or options (with the exception of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/bytecountformatter/units/1408069-usebytes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", which would generate "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "Zero bytes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ").The result is appropriate for standalone output.  "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Special handling of certain values such as zero is especially important in some languages, so it's highly recommended that this property be left in its default state."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Default value is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
